        <h2>Ferni vs ChatGPT</h2>
        <p>ChatGPT is incredible for tasks—writing emails, coding, research. But for personal growth? It's a generalist that forgets you after each session.</p>
        <p>Ferni is built specifically for coaching. It <strong>remembers your journey</strong>, <strong>responds instantly</strong>, and brings in <strong>specialized expertise</strong> when you need it. Plus, you can just call a phone number—no typing required.</p>
      </div>
