    <div class="compare-detail reveal">
      <div class="compare-detail__content">
        <h2>Ferni vs Replika</h2>
        <p>Replika is designed for companionship and entertainment. That's a valid use case, but it's not what Ferni does.</p>
        <p>Ferni is focused on <strong>your growth</strong>. Every conversation moves you forward—whether that's managing stress, making decisions, or building habits. It's coaching, not chat.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="compare-detail reveal">
      <div class="compare-detail__content">
        <h2>Ferni vs Human Coaching</h2>
        <p>Human coaches are wonderful—but they're expensive, have limited availability, and require scheduling in advance.</p>
        <p>Ferni is always available. It costs a fraction of human coaching. And because it remembers everything, you never have to catch your coach up on context. That said—Ferni isn't a replacement for therapy or clinical support when you need it.</p>
